title: Naturasi Cucina Bio
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Italian, Organic, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Part of the Naturasi network, serves organic food with plenty of vegan dishes (including desserts) which are clearly marked. Lots of space. Free Wi-Fi. Cafeteria during the day and restaurant in the evening. Previously named Bioesseri by Naturasi.
